{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"FileReader","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/FileReader","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/File_API\">File API <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/FileReader\"><code>FileReader</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/FileReader\"><code>FileReader()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/FileReader/error\"><code>error</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readyState\"><code>readyState</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/result\"><code>result</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/abort\"><code>abort()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsArrayBuffer\"><code>readAsArrayBuffer()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsBinaryString\"><code>readAsBinaryString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsDataURL\"><code>readAsDataURL()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsText\"><code>readAsText()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/abort_event\"><code>abort</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/error_event\"><code>error</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/load_event\"><code>load</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/loadend_event\"><code>loadend</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/loadstart_event\"><code>loadstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/progress_event\"><code>progress</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Related pages for File API</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/FileList\"><code>FileList</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReaderSync\"><code>FileReaderSync</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/URL/createObjectURL\"><code>URL.createObjectURL()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/URL/revokeObjectURL\"><code>URL.revokeObjectURL()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>藉由 <code>FileReader</code> 物件，Web 應用程式能以非同步（asynchronously）方式讀取儲存在用戶端的檔案（或原始資料暫存）內容，可以使用 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a> 或 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> 物件指定要讀取的資料。</p>\n<p>File 物件可以從使用者於 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/HTML/Element/input\"><code>&lt;input&gt;</code></a> 元素選擇之檔案所回傳的 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/FileList\"><code>FileList</code></a> 物件當中取得，或是來自<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/HTML_Drag_and_Drop_API\">拖放操作</a>所產生的 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/DataTransfer\"><code>DataTransfer</code></a> 物件之中，也能由 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement</code></a> 物件（元素物件）執行 <code>mozGetAsFile()</code> 方法後回傳。</p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> This feature is available in <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers</a></p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"建構式","title":"建構式","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"filereader_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/FileReader\"><code>FileReader()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>建立新的 <code>FileReader</code> 物件。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>\n<p>請參考<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/File_API/Using_files_from_web_applications\">在網頁應用程式中使用本地檔案</a>的更多細節與範例。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"屬性","title":"屬性","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"filereader.error\"><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/FileReader/error\"><code>FileReader.error</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>此 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMException\"><code>DOMException</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> 類型的物件記錄了讀取資料時發生的錯誤資訊。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"filereader.readystate\"><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readyState\"><code>FileReader.readyState</code></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>表示目前 <code>FileReader</code> 狀態的數字，其代表的意義為：</p>\n    <table>\n      <tbody>\n        <tr>\n          <td><code>EMPTY</code></td>\n          <td><code>0</code></td>\n          <td>尚未讀入任何資料。</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td><code>LOADING</code></td>\n          <td><code>1</code></td>\n          <td>正在讀入資料。</td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n          <td><code>DONE</code></td>\n          <td><code>2</code></td>\n          <td>完成資料讀取。</td>\n        </tr>\n      </tbody>\n    </table>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"filereader.result_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/result\"><code>FileReader.result</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>讀入的資料內容。只有在讀取完成之後此屬性才有效，而資料的格式則取決於是由哪一個方法進行讀取。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"事件處理器","title":"事件處理器","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"filereader.onabort_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/abort_event\"><code>FileReader.onabort</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLMediaElement/abort_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">abort (en-US)</a></code> 事件處理器，於讀取被中斷時觸發。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"filereader.onerror_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/error_event\"><code>FileReader.onerror</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/error_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">error (en-US)</a></code> 事件處理器，於讀取發生錯誤時觸發。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"filereader.onload_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/load_event\"><code>FileReader.onload</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/load_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">load (en-US)</a></code> 事件處理器，於讀取完成時觸發。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"filereader.onloadstart\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>FileReader.onloadstart</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/loadstart_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">loadstart (en-US)</a></code> 事件處理器，於讀取開始時觸發。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"filereader.onloadend\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>FileReader.onloadend</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/loadend_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">loadend (en-US)</a></code> 事件處理器，於每一次讀取結束之後觸發（不論成功或失敗），會於 <code>onload</code> 或 <code>onerror</code> 事件處理器之後才執行。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"filereader.onprogress\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>FileReader.onprogress</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/progress_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">progress (en-US)</a></code> 事件處理器，於讀取 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a> 內容時觸發。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\">\n  <p><strong>備註：</strong> <code>FileReader</code> 物件繼承自 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a>，其所有的事件也都能夠透過 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\" title=\"addEventListener\"><code>addEventListener</code></a> 方法來註冊事件監聽器。</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"方法","title":"方法","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"filereader.abort_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/abort\"><code>FileReader.abort()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>中斷目前的讀取，此方法回傳後屬性 <code>readyState</code> 將會是 <code>DONE</code>。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"filereader.readasarraybuffer_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsArrayBuffer\"><code>FileReader.readAsArrayBuffer()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>開始讀取指定的 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a>，讀取完成後屬性 <code>result</code> 將以 <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>ArrayBuffer</code></a> 物件來表示讀入的資料內容。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"filereader.readasbinarystring_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsBinaryString\"><code>FileReader.readAsBinaryString()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>開始讀取指定的 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a>，讀取完成後屬性 <code>result</code> 將以字串型式來表示讀入的原始二進位資料（raw binary data）。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"filereader.readasdataurl_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsDataURL\"><code>FileReader.readAsDataURL()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>開始讀取指定的 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a>，讀取完成後屬性 <code>result</code> 將以 <code>data:</code> URL 格式（base64 編碼）的字串來表示讀入的資料內容。</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"filereader.readastext_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/readAsText\"><code>FileReader.readAsText()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>開始讀取指定的 <a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a>，讀取完成後屬性 <code>result</code> 將以文字字串型式來表示讀入的資料內容。</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"規範","id":"規範","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/FileAPI/#APIASynch","title":"File API"}],"query":"api.FileReader"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"瀏覽器相容性","id":"瀏覽器相容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.FileReader","dataURL":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/FileReader/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"參見","title":"參見","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/File_API/Using_files_from_web_applications\">在網頁應用程式中使用本地檔案</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/File\"><code>File</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/Blob\"><code>Blob</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"建構式","id":"建構式"},{"text":"屬性","id":"屬性"},{"text":"方法","id":"方法"},{"text":"規範","id":"規範"},{"text":"瀏覽器相容性","id":"瀏覽器相容性"},{"text":"參見","id":"參見"}],"summary":"藉由 FileReader 物件，Web 應用程式能以非同步（asynchronously）方式讀取儲存在用戶端的檔案（或原始資料暫存）內容，可以使用 File 或 Blob 物件指定要讀取的資料。","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"FileReader","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"FileReader","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"FileReader","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"FileReader","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"FileReader","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"FileReader","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"FileReader","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"FileReader","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/web/api/filereader","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/web/api/filereader/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web","title":"給開發者的網頁技術文件"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API","title":"Web APIs"},{"uri":"/zh-TW/docs/Web/API/FileReader","title":"FileReader"}],"pageTitle":"FileReader - Web APIs | MDN","noIndexing":false}}